Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara daren yau ne a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne farkon gangamin Trump na biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, tare da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake hana kuri'un tabbatar da zabensa don cike gurbin kotun koli, Trump na da niyyar samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na tsoron rasa iko a kan majalisar dokoki lokacin da za a kada kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai kasance a daren yau kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma ET yau da dare, Asabar, Satumba 29, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump na iya jawabi a wannan makon a gaban kotun koli don zabar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai tsanani saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i, wanda ya hana kuri'ar tabbatar da majalisar dattijai da ake tsammani na mako guda don binciken FBI.
Amma babban manufar wannan gangamin shi ne don taimakawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
A cewar kamfen din Trump, taron gangamin da za a yi a mako mai zuwa zai taimaka wajen karfafa gwiwa tsakanin masu ba da agaji da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma karawa majalisa da majalisar wakilai rinjaye.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajanda, don haka yayin da muke ci gaba da wannan lokacin kamfen, shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama", in ji mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda bai bayyana sunansa ba, ya shaida wa Reuters.
Rally din da aka shirya a gidan wasan WesBanco Arena a Wheeling na iya kawo magoya baya da yawa daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma su sami ɗaukar hoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta yi la'akari.
Wannan zai zama ziyarar Asabar ta biyu ga West Virginia a cikin wata guda, jihar da ta lashe ta da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya yi baya a zaben.
"Wannan ba kyakkyawan alama ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa zai zo ya taimaka masa a wannan zaben", in ji masanin kimiyyar siyasa na Jami'ar West Virginia, Simon Hader, in ji Reuters.
