Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce jam'iyyar farko da ta amince da wannan ra'ayin ba, jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki kwana hudu a mako a yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
Duk da haka, wannan burin ba a biya shi ba a jam'iyyar Labour.
