Menene bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya kuma shin sun yi wani abu don kawar da talauci?
A ranar Asabar mai zuwa, za a gudanar da bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara na Global Citizen Festival a New York, wanda zai ba da babbar dama ga manyan taurari, kuma babban burin bikin shine kawar da talauci a duniya.
A wannan shekara ta bakwai ta bikin na Global Citizen, za a ga dubban miliyoyin mutane sun taru a kan babban filin shakatawa na Central Park ba kawai don jin daɗin ayyukan zane-zane na Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don yada ainihin manufar bikin, wato kawar da talauci a duniya nan da shekarar 2030.
An fara bikin ne a shekarar 2012 kuma wannan bikin ya fadada kungiyar Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan ta kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun damar shiga taron kyauta (idan ba ku son siyan tikiti na VIP), masu sauraron bikin dole ne suyi wasu ayyuka ko kuma jerin "ayyuka" kamar yin aikin sa kai don yada manufar kawar da duniya, aika imel, yin waya ga wani shugaban duniya, ko yin wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ya samu a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage kafin cimma burin?
Ra'ayin shirya wa jama'a waƙoƙi kyauta hanya ce ta gaskiya don sa mutane su ɗauki mataki ko kuma wani nau'in abin da ake kira "zaɓin zaɓi" - wanda mutane ke tsammanin yin rajista ko aika saƙon Twitter yana da wani bambanci?
Global Citizen ya ce tun daga shekarar 2011, masu goyon bayansa sun yi fiye da "aiki" miliyan 19 don dalilai daban-daban.
Ya ce ayyukansa sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawarin samar da kudade da manufofi na dala biliyan 3.7 ko sama da haka, wanda zai shafi mutane sama da biliyan 225 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta gabatar da alkawura da kuma sanarwar 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukanta, wanda a kalla dala biliyan 1 aka riga aka rarraba ko tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka samu sun shafi rayukan mutane kusan miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da Power of Nutrition. Power of Nutrition wata kungiya ce ta masu saka jari da masu shirya shirye-shirye a Burtaniya, wadanda ke "taimaka wa kananan yara su bunkasa zuwa cikakkiyar damar su" kuma bayan an samu sakonnin Twitter sama da 4,700 daga mazauna duniya, sun yi alkawarin bada dala miliyan 35 ga kasar ta Rwanda don kawo karshen matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki.
