Sakataren rikon kwarya na Amurka zai iya amfani da sojojin Amurka don "kulle" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha
Sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Ryan Zinke ya bayyana cewa Washington za ta yi amfani da sojan ruwa "idan ya cancanta" don hana makamashi na Rasha isa wasu kasuwannin, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Washington Examiner.
Zinc ya yi zargin cewa shigar Rasha cikin Syria - musamman ma inda Rasha ke aiki a gayyatar da gwamnatin ta ke yi - don neman sabbin kasuwannin makamashi ne.
"Dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine saboda ina ganin suna son yin amfani da makamashi kamar Gabashin Turai, Kudancin Turai", in ji Zinke.
