Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da 'tallace-tallace na talla' don 'ƙara'
Wata mako bayan da wata jarida ta kasar Sin ta wallafa wata talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke nuna amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya yi tir da amfani da kafofin yada labaran Amurka wajen yada farfagandar da ke kan Beijing.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya yi ikirarin cewa China ta yi tasiri a zaben majalisar dattijai na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, wanda China ta musanta - jaridar da ta fi amfani da ita a jihar Iowa - ta yi nuni da wadatar da aka biya ta jaridar kasar Sin a cikin Des Moines Register.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa China ta yi kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, wani sabon babi ne a cikin kokarin da Washington ke yi na matsawa kasar Sin lamba, kamar yadda jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters.
Ko da yake baƙon gwamnati na iya yin tallace-tallace don haɓaka kasuwanci, amma a halin yanzu akwai yaƙin cinikayya tsakanin Beijing da Washington wanda ke haifar da ƙarin haraji kan shigo da kayayyaki.
Masana kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce, farashin da China ta sanya a farkon yakin cinikayya an tsara shi ne don shafar masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican.
Gwamnan Iowa na dogon lokaci, wanda ke fitar da kayayyakin gona da yawa zuwa China, Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikata, manoma da kasuwancin Amurka.
A wata kasida a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya rubuta cewa, "China yanzu tana yin amfani da tallace-tallace na tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu ta kyauta".
"Gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da jarida ta hanyar tallata tallace-tallace a Des Moines don yada kamfen dinta", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, jaridu da aka sanya don sayarwa a titunan Beijing ba su da wata ma'ana ta adawa kuma ba su nuna ainihin ra'ayoyin jama'ar kasar Sin game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminisanci ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa "wani babban jaridar kasar Sin ta yi watsi da tayin buga labarinsa", amma bai bayyana sunan jaridar ba.
