Mahaifin yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin samar da sabuwar hanyar sadarwa don yin gogayya da Google da Facebook.
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi, yana shirin kaddamar da wani kamfani da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin sanannen masanin fasaha, Inerpt, kamfani ne wanda aka gina akan dandamali na tushen budewa na Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda za su ba da damar shiga.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ta bayyana cewa babban burin Inertip shi ne "mamaye duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi wannan yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan app ɗin yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "Kayan adana bayanan kan layi na sirri" ko POD.
Za su iya kasancewa jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalandarku, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na kasuwanci.
Wannan yana nufin cewa Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda kuma suna nan a lokaci guda.
Wani abu mai ban sha'awa game da adana bayanan sirri a kan layi shine cewa mai amfani zai iya yanke shawarar abin da zai yi amfani da shi.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafawa ta mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inertip ita ce samar da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewar da ta dace don samar da ingantaccen aiki ga kowa.
Kamfanin ya hada da wani dandamali na tsaro wanda aka saya daga Berners-Lee, Bruce, IBM, ma'aikata na wasu masu haɓaka waɗanda aka ba da kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu coding masu sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da aka samo akan gidan yanar gizon Inert.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa "ba sa magana da Facebook da Google game da ko za su kawo canji mai girma wanda zai lalata duk tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
"Ba ma neman izinin su".
A wani rubutu da aka buga a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inertip "na nufin samar da wutar lantarki da tsarin halittu na kasuwanci don taimakawa wajen kiyaye mutunci da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo wanda aka gina a kan daskararru".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ta kawo sauyi a yanar gizo ta hanyar kafa kungiyar World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama babbar murya a cikin muhawarar tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da lokacin da aka ƙaddamar da Inertip, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai kafa da kuma darektan Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da zamani na gaba na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard von: Yaƙin Duniya na Farko
An yi bikin asalinsa shekaru 100 bayan haka don girmama limamin cocin Ingila wanda ya lashe giciye Victoria a matsayin jarumi a yakin duniya na farko.
Lt. Col. The Reverend Bernard Vaughn ya lashe lambar yabo a lokacin da aka kai hari a Belenglis da Lehcourt a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918.
Duk da haka, bayan kwana hudu, wani soja da ke tsare a cikin fursuna ya harbe shi kuma bai san cewa ya sami babbar lambar yabo ta sojojin Birtaniya ba.
A ranar Asabar, a wani fareti a Rushden, Northamptonshire, jikokinsa biyu sun kaddamar da wani dutse mai daraja a gare shi.
Wani jikansa, Michael Vaughn ya ce, "Wannan abin al'ajabi ne" a lokacin da aka bude wannan dutsen bayan shekaru 100 da nasarar da kakansa ya samu.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Colonel Vaughn ya ja-goranci rukunin sojojinsa zuwa gabar Canal de Saint-Quentin "a cikin hayaki mai yawa da kuma harbi mai yawa daga filin yaƙi da kuma bindigogi masu yawa", in ji jaridar London Gazette.
Daga nan sai ya koma layin wuta kuma ya ci gaba da jagorantar layin "da ƙarfin hali" kafin ya ci nasara da rukunin sojoji uku da kansa, yana fuskantar bindigogi a fagen fama.
An kashe Lt. Col. Von a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918 - kusan wata daya kafin ƙarshen yaƙin.
Michael Vaughn, mai shekara 72, ya ce aikin kakansa "wani abu ne da ba zan taɓa iya yi ba amma abin ban mamaki ne".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vaughn sun kuma ba da furanni bayan bikin da aka yi da ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial.
Michael Vaughn ya ce, "Na ji daɗin halartar wannan faretin", ya kuma ce, "Tallafin da mutane da yawa suka bayar ya nuna ƙarfin hali na jarumi na gaske".
