Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji ba shi da 'yanci' daga jima'i
Mai tsalle-tsalle na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce jinsi ya sa ya ji ya fi kowa ƙanƙanta - amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Daily, mai shekara 24, ta ce, "Ba kowa ba ne kamar ni, sai da na shiga makarantar sakandare".
Da yake magana a kan Rediyo 4 Desert Island Discs, wanda Lauren LaVerne ya gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin' yan luwadi don ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce, kasancewa iyaye ya rage musu farin cikin lashe gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da wasan kwaikwayon na dogon lokaci, Kirsty Young ya ɗauki hutu na watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Da yake bayyana a matsayin wanda aka ware a taron farko na Laverne, Daily ya ce ya girma yana jin "ƙarancin" idan aka kwatanta da kowa, saboda "ba a yarda da jama'a su so yara maza da mata ba".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, jin kasawa da kuma bambancin da nake da shi ne babban abin da ya ba ni ƙarfin yin nasara".
Ya ce yana son ya nuna musu cewa shi "wani ne" don kada mutane su yi sanyin gwiwa sa'ad da suka san ko shi ɗan luwaɗi ne.
Daily, wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla sau biyu a gasar Olympics, ya zama babban mai tallata LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da kasancewar sa a gasar Commonwealth ta wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don yin kira ga ƙarin ƙasashe da su daina ɗaukar luwadi a matsayin laifi.
Ya ce ya yi magana ne domin yana ganin cewa yana da sa'a ya rayu cikin 'yanci ba tare da tsoron sakamakon ayyukansa ba kuma yana son wasu su nuna masa "bege".
Wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku ya ce, "ya ba ni mamaki" da yadda mutumin da ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013 ya ƙaunaci Dustin Lance Black, wani mai shirya fina-finai a Amurka.
Daley ya yi aure a shekarar da ta gabata ga wani wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar, wanda ya girme shi da shekara 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru ba matsala ba ce.
"Lokacin da kuka sha wahala sosai a wannan lokacin" - ya halarci gasar Olympics a karo na farko yana ɗan shekara 14 kuma bayan shekaru uku mahaifinsa ya mutu daga cutar kansa - ya ce yana da wuya a sami mutumin da ya ga irin wannan tashin hankali.
Ma'auratan sun haifi Robert Ray Black-Daley a watan Yuni, kuma Daley ya ce "dukkanin ra'ayinsu" ya canza.
Ya ce, "Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, da na ce, 'Ina son lashe lambar zinare.'
"Ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinaren Olympics muhimmanci.
Robby ne zinariyar Olympics na".
Sun sa wa ɗansu suna Robert bayan mahaifinsa, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 daga ciwon daji na kwakwalwa yana da shekaru 40.
Daily ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya yi a karshe shi ne tambayarsa ko yana da tikiti zuwa London 2012 - domin yana son zama a jere na gaba.
Ya ce: "Ban gaya musu cewa ba za su iya zama a jere na gaba ba, Baba.
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya yi numfashi na ƙarshe, kuma ban tabbata cewa ba za a iya cin nasara ba har sai da numfashinsa ya tsaya kuma ya mutu", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daly ta lashe lambar tagulla a gasar Olympics ta 2012.
"Na san cewa babu abin da zai iya zama mafi girma fiye da abin da na yi mafarkin rayuwata - yin iyo a wasannin Olympics a gaban masu kallo a gida", in ji shi.
Wannan ita ce waƙar da ya fara rairawa, Proud by Heather Small, wanda ya yi daidai da yadda yake shirya gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu yana da ƙarfi a hannunsa.
