Furik da kansa ya juya wasan zuwa "mu'ujizar rana" ta Turai, kafin wannan rashin nasara, a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙungiyar nasara a ɓangarorin biyu na babban juyin juya halin ranar ƙarshe.
