An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
An yi alkawarin cewa za a fara amfani da sabon jirgin ruwan yakin Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma saboda rashin tsari da tsada, ba za a fara amfani da shi ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
Rahoton Die Zeit ya ruwaito wani kakakin soji yana cewa an dage aikin Rhaeland-Fage, babban jirgin ruwa na rukunin Baden-Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya wannan jirgi zai shiga cikin Sojojin Ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsaloli masu tasowa bayan bayarwa sun sanya makomar wannan babban shiri ta zama ta baya.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg da rundunar sojin ruwa ta umarce su a shekarar 2007 za su maye gurbin na'urorin yakin Breemen.
Ana tsammanin zai ƙunshi babban bindiga, rukunin anti-aircraft da anti-ship missile, da wasu fasahohin ɓoye kamar radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran mahimman fasalulluka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - sabbin jiragen ruwa na yaƙi dole ne su iya yin aiki daga tashar jiragen ruwa na gida har tsawon shekaru biyu.
Koyaya, jinkiri mai ɗorewa yana nufin cewa jirgin yaƙin zamani - wanda zai ba Jamus damar nuna ƙarfinta a teku - zai riga ya zama tsohon yayi lokacin da ya shiga sabis, in ji Die Zeit.
An yi ta magana game da mummunan yakin F125 a bara, lokacin da jami'an sojan ruwan Jamus suka ƙi yin amfani da jirgin kuma suka mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin jirgin ruwa na Lom & Foss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojan ruwa ta dawo da jirgin zuwa kamfanin kera jirgin ruwa bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a sami cikakken bayani game da dalilan dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ce akwai wasu manyan "kurakurai na software da kayan aiki" da suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani don turawa kan ayyukan yaƙi.
Rashin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci, saboda jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg zai kasance da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - rabin ma'aikata a kan tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Breemen.
Hakanan, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma ba zai yiwu a ci gaba da inganta shi ba a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa "Rhyland-Phage" mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin sama - ya zama matsala.
Ya tashi daga farkon €2.2 biliyan zuwa €3.1 biliyan ($3.6 biliyan) mai ban mamaki.
Matsalolin da suka taso a cikin sabon jirgin ruwa na musamman suna da mahimmanci a yayin da ake nuna cewa sojojin ruwan Jamus suna raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus Hans-Peter Bartels ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa suna da gaske "suna ƙarancin jiragen ruwa masu aiki".
Jami'in ya ce matsalar tana kara saurin bunkasa yayin da lokaci ke wucewa saboda an kashe tsofaffin jiragen ruwa, amma ba a maye gurbin su da sabbin jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi nadamar cewa babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg da ya dace da shiga cikin jirgin ruwa.
Ƙungiyar National Trust ta ji labarin rayuwar ɓoye na waɗannan tsuntsaye
An yi wani sabon bincike a tsaunukan Scotland don a gano yadda jemage ke amfani da ƙasa don neman abinci.
Ana fatan cewa sabon binciken zai ba da sabon haske game da halayyar dabbar mai tashi mai ban mamaki kuma zai taimaka wajen jagorantar ayyukan kiyayewa na gaba.
Binciken da masu bincike daga National Trust of Scotland suka yi zai bi sawun talakawa da Soprano Pipistrelles da kuma fararen kunne masu dogon kunne da Dabbenton a cikin Inverieve Gardens a West Ross.
Za a sanya sauti na musamman a wurare masu mahimmanci a kan dukiyar don lura da ayyukan kifin a duk tsawon kakar.
Ma'aikatan NHS da masu sa kai za su kuma gudanar da binciken wayar hannu ta amfani da na'urorin gano abubuwa.
Masana binciken sauti na duk masu son sauti za su tantance yawan kiran da ake yi da kuma abin da nau'in ke yi.
Za a tsara taswirar mazaunin halitta da rahoto daga baya don samar da cikakken hoto game da halayensu a kan sikelin ƙasa.
Mashawarcin kare muhalli na NTS, Rob Dever, yana fatan sakamakon zai bayyana wane yanki na mazaunin halitta ne ke da mahimmanci ga jemage da yadda kowane nau'in ke amfani da shi.
Wannan bayanin zai taimaka wajen tantance fa'idodin ayyukan kula da mazaunin halitta kamar samar da wuraren kiwo da kuma yadda za a kiyaye wuraren da ke da gandun daji don bat da sauran nau'ikan da suka danganci su.
A cikin ƙarni na ƙarshe, yawan ƙudaje a Scotland da Ingila ya ragu sosai.
An yi garkuwa da su saboda lalacewar mazaunin da aka yi da kuma asarar mazaunin halitta da aka yi ta hanyar gine-gine da ayyukan ci gaba.
Turbin iska da walƙiya ma suna da haɗari, da wasu hanyoyin sarrafa sinadarai na takarda mai tashi da kayan gini, da kuma hare-haren da ke faruwa a cikin gidajen dabbobi.
Ba sa iya ganin kome.
Duk da haka, saboda halayensu na farauta da dare, kunnuwansu sun fi idanunsu amfani wajen kama ganima.
Suna amfani da fasahar gano wuri don gano kwari da abubuwan da ke cikin hanyarsu.
