2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, 2004, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh, a arewacin Sumatra, a ƙasar Indonesia, ta haddasa tsunami a ƙasashe 14, kuma ta kashe mutane 226,000, fiye da rabin mutanen da ke Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: A shekara ta 2006, guguwar tsunami mai girman awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: A shekara ta 2009, an yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: A shekara ta 2010, an yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 a Mentawai, a Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin PD Jaya da ke Aceh, inda ta lalata abubuwa da yawa kuma ta haifar da yanayi na tsoro, inda rushewar ta tunatar da mutane game da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu wata guguwar tsunami da ta faru a lokacin, amma gine-gine da yawa sun rushe kuma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Indonesiya na Lombok, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a makale na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Paulin da laifin cin zarafin mata
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sara Palin, bisa zargin kisan kai.
A cewar rahoton da hukumomin jihar Alaska suka fitar, an kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma zargin sa baki kan rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma adawa da tsare shi.
Rahotanni sun ce, lokacin da wata mace da ta san ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton aikata laifi, sai ya kwace wayar daga hannun ta.
Ana tsare Palin a gidan Mart-Su Pre-Trial Facility kuma ana ba shi belin $500, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Rahotanni a kafafen yada labarai sun ce, an gurfanar da shi a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda a lokacin da ake tuhumarsa ya bayyana kansa "ba shi da laifi".
Palin zai fuskanci laifin mataki na uku, wanda ke nufin zai iya fuskantar ɗaurin shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin aikata laifi na biyu, wanda ya kai shi gidan yari na kwana daya da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da ake tuhumar Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa Todd Paulin hari.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Paulin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton harin.
A halin yanzu, wannan shari'ar tana gaban Kotun Tsohon Sojojin Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, da tsoma baki wajen bayar da rahoton aikata laifukan cin zarafin mata, da kuma shan giya a lokacin da ake zarginsa da aikata wannan laifin.
Abokinsa ta zarge shi da cewa ya buge ta a fuska.
Wasu kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji sun soki Sarah Palin a shekarar 2016 bayan da ta danganta tashin hankali da PTSD da danta ya samu daga aikinsa a Iraki.
