Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ba da gargadin farko ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da China ke fitarwa ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminium.
Wannan makon ya yi matukar karuwa tare da sabbin haraji da suka shafi dala biliyan 200 (£ 150bn) a cikin darajar, ana sanya haraji a kan dukkan kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta yi tsayayya da wannan ta hanyar biyan haraji tsakanin kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari kan kayayyakin da Amurka ta shigo da su, wanda ya fi dala biliyan 60 a baya-bayan nan.
China ta sha alwashin bin sahun Amurka kuma ba za a taba watsi da ita ba a matsayin babbar tattalin arzikin duniya nan ba da jimawa ba.
Da zarar Washington ta yi watsi da bukatar, to za ta yi matukar damuwa ga shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta iya yin wasan ta yadda ya kamata, to, China za ta iya ba da tallafi mai kyau na dogon lokaci, ta rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu, saboda matsin lamba daga yaƙe-yaƙe na kasuwanci a Amurka.
A zahiri, madauki na tattalin arziki da zai fara a ɗayan ƙasashe idan aka yanke shawara ta siyasa cikin gaggawa a Washington ko Beijing ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda mutane suka ɗauka a baya, "in ji Abigail Grace, wani abokin bincike wanda ke mai da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Sabuwar Amurka a Cibiyar Nazarin Tsaro.
Ministan harkokin wajen ya ce Syria a shirye take ta mayar da 'yan gudun hijirar.
Syria ta shirya ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai, kuma sun nemi taimako don sake gina kasar da ta lalace sakamakon yakin da ya shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
A lokacin da yake jawabi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Mulem ya ce halin da ake ciki a kasar na samun sauki.
Ya ce, "Yau, ci gaban da aka samu wajen yaki da ta'addanci ya sa yanayin yankinmu ya fi karko da tsaro".
Don inganta yanayin al'ada, Gwamnati ta fara sake gina wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata.
Yanzu duk yanayin ya shirya don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da suka tsere daga kasarmu saboda ta'addanci da matakan tattalin arziki na yau da kullun da ke fuskantar rayuwarsu da rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya barke a 2011.
Akwai wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar da ke bukatar agaji.
Al-Ma'alem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta taimaka wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai yarda da tallafi ko taimako daga kasashen da ke ba da tallafi ba.
Turai ta buga gasar Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
A Le Golf National a wajen birnin Paris, Faransa, kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta doke Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5.
Amurka ta sha kaye sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Ta hanyar ci gaba da ci gaba har zuwa maki 14.5 da ake bukata don doke Amurka, dan wasan Denmark Thomas Bajern ya sake lashe gasar Turai.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson ya yi gwagwarmaya a wasanni da yawa, ya jefa kwallo a rami na 16 na Par-3 kuma ya ci Francesco Molinari.
Gwanin golf na Italiya Molinari ya zama dan wasa na farko a cikin 'yan wasa hudu da ya haskaka a duk fa'idodi, kuma ya ci gaba da 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Denmark Thorbjørn Olesen, wanda ya kasance dan wasa mafi karancin kudi a kungiyar ta Turai, ya kori dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth da ci 5-4.
Dustin Johnson, wanda shine dan wasan da ya fi kowacce kasa daraja a duniya, ya fadi a raga da Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya zama dan wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup.
Tsohon ɗan wasan Ryder Cup takwas, Sergio Garcia na Spain ya zama zakaran Turai na kowane lokaci tare da maki 25.5.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma babu abin da zan iya yi a yau.
Wannan shekara ce mai wahala.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya amince da ni.
Ina farin ciki da na dawo da kofin.
Wannan game da ƙungiyar ne kuma ina farin cikin cewa na sami damar taimakawa, "in ji Garcia mai motsin rai bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya mika wutar ga dan wasansa John Rahm wanda ya doke Tiger Woods a wasan daya a ranar Lahadi da ci 2-1.
Rahm, ɗan shekara 23, ya ce, "Ina alfahari sosai da na ci Tiger Woods, mutumin da na girma ina kallo".
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da tarihin Ryder Cup na 13-21-3.
"Wani babban ɗan wasa ya faɗi wani adadi mai ban mamaki, Jack Nicklaus ya lashe manyan kofuna 14 kawai".
Sai dai 'yan wasan golf masu inganci a duk gasar, Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, kungiyar ta Amurka ta yi tafiya a duk karshen mako don neman hanyar adalci.
Shugaban Amurka Jim Furyk ya yi tsokaci game da rashin nasarar da tawagar ta samu, "Ina alfahari da wadannan mutane, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
Mun yi kokarin matsa wa kungiyar Turai lamba a safiyar yau.
