Sabuntawa na Red Tide: Yawan Pinealus, Manatee da Sarsoto sun ragu sosai.
Rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa yawan adadin Red Tide a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu sosai.
A cewar FWC, ana samun rahoton yanayin Patchier Bloom a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties - wanda ke haifar da raguwar taro.
Ruwa mai tsananin zafi ya mamaye gabar teku mai nisan mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudancin Lee County.
An gano wasu wurare a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a cikin ƙananan wurare fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma samu wasu cututtuka a cikin yankin Pasco.
"A cikin makon da ya gabata an ba da rahoton matsakaitan ma'auni a cikin Pinellas County ko bakin teku, ƙananan zuwa manyan ma'auni a bakin teku na Hilleborough County, manyan ma'auni daga bango a cikin Manatee County, manyan ma'auni daga bango a kan babbar hanya ko bakin teku a Sarasota County, matsakaitan ma'auni daga bango a Charlotte County, manyan ma'auni daga bango a Lee County ko bakin teku, da ƙananan ma'auni a cikin Collier County.
Rahotanni na ci gaba da samun matsalar numfashi a Pinellas, Manette, Sarasota, Lee da Collier Counties.
Ba a samu rahoton cutar numfashi ba a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
